{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">PinDrop: Escape The Room is a single-player horror adventure that thrusts you into a dark, procedurally generated world where zombies hunt by sound. Survival depends on absolute silence, making stealth your only weapon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The question isn\u2019t just if you\u2019ll survive, but how long you can play before the undead catch up. Among the four exits, one of the four doors is the true door, your only path to freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/ESCAPE.gif?t=1731937061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Relentless Tension</strong> \u2013 Enter an immersive nightmare world where every sound could be your last. Hide, move carefully, and stay silent to avoid terrifying encounters with the undead.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/Your.gif?t=1731937061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unpredictable World</strong> \u2013 Explore a landscape that constantly shifts with random object spawns and nonlinear paths, ensuring no two playthroughs are ever the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032460/extras/optimized_nightmare.gif?t=1731937061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Light Mechanics</strong> \u2013 Your torch can guide or betray you. Scavenge batteries, use light carefully, and balance survival with silence to outwit your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready for a brutal, sound sensitive journey that will test your n